---

<Layout
  title="About Cycle Paradise | Cycling Tour Experts in Sri Lanka"
  description="Meet the guides, makers, and sustainability partners behind Cycle Paradise. Discover our mission, values, rider care standards, and community impact across Sri Lanka."
  keywords={["about cycle paradise", "cycling guides sri lanka", "sri lanka bike tours company"]}
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 via-white to-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-600 font-semibold">Who We Are</p>
          <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
            Riders, storytellers, and guardians of Sri Lanka's open roads.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Cycle Paradise was born on a misty morning climb through the Knuckles range. Today we operate island-wide cycling expeditions
            that braid performance riding with deep cultural exchange. Our guides, mechanics, nutritionists, and local artisans operate as one
            studio to craft journeys that are safe, soulful, and sustainable.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a
              href="/packages"
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-primary-600 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors"
            >
              Browse Tours
              <svg class="ml-3 h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:border-primary-400 hover:text-primary-600"
            >
              Talk to a Trip Designer
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-primary-100 bg-white/80 shadow-xl backdrop-blur">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100">
            {missionStats.map((item) => (
              <div class="p-6">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">{item.value}</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">{item.label}</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">{item.detail}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-600 font-semibold">Our Mission</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Build legendary rides that uplift every village we roll through.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            We curate every expedition with three guardrails: safety that rivals ProTour support, meaningful encounters with craftspeople and
            conservationists, and regenerative operations that keep Sri Lanka thriving for decades of cyclists to come.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mt-1 mr-3 inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">1</span>
              <p>Dynamic route intelligence that adapts weather, traffic, and rider energy in real time.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mt-1 mr-3 inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">2</span>
              <p>Hands-on cultural playbooks co-created with historians, tea masters, and wildlife trackers.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mt-1 mr-3 inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-600">3</span>
              <p>Impact commitments that track carbon, fair wages, and rider wellbeing metrics each quarter.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Values in Motion</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">These are the promises every Cycle Paradise team member trains to uphold.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            {values.map((value) => (
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-100">
                <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-50 text-primary-600">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={value.icon}></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">{value.title}</h4>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">{value.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-900 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-300 font-semibold">Leadership Team</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Meet the riders guiding every decision.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-300">
            We blend expedition know-how, hospitality craft, and business rigor. Every leader still rides at least two tours a quarter to stay close to riders.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900">
          Book a discovery call
          <svg class="ml-3 h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        {leadershipTeam.map((lead) => (
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-6 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-primary-200">{lead.role}</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">{lead.name}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-200">{lead.experience}</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-300">Focus: {lead.focus}</p>
            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {lead.badges.map((badge) => (
                <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-100">
                  {badge}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-600 font-semibold">Timeline</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Milestones that shaped us.</h2>
          <ol class="mt-8 space-y-6 border-l-2 border-primary-100 pl-6">
            {milestones.map((milestone) => (
              <li>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="relative -ml-[43px] mt-0.5 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white ring-2 ring-primary-200">
                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">{milestone.year}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">{milestone.title}</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">{milestone.description}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-primary-50 p-8">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-700 font-semibold">Impact Snapshots</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Proof that mindful travel works.</h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
            {impactHighlights.map((impact) => (
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-primary-100">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-700">{impact.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">{impact.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-600 font-semibold">Your Next Ride</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Ready for the story you will tell after your ride?</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Whether you are planning a corporate retreat, celebrating a milestone, or testing your endurance, our trip designers build a ride narrative that matches your why.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-3 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Multilingual guides and cultural hosts
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-3 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Nutrition, recovery, and gear concierge
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-3 h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Community investments built into every booking
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-primary-600 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow hover:bg-primary-700">
              Plan a Custom Tour
            </a>
            <a href="/guides" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary-600">
              Explore Route Guides
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[32px] bg-white p-10 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-100">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 font-semibold">Talk to us</p>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Schedule a free planning session</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">Share your riding style, time frame, and dream scenery. We will send a customized ride playbook within 48 hours.</p>
          <dl class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">Email</dt>
              <dd class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">info@cycleparadise.lk</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">Phone</dt>
              <dd class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">+94 77 123 4567</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">Studio</dt>
              <dd class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">38/12 Temple Lane, Colombo 05, Sri Lanka</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
